node.text:
Where the bonnet magic happens ✨ Did you know that our bonnets are thoughtfully made in our Vancouver, WA studio? Every Briar bonnet is crafted with love + care by our in-house production team, and our hope is that you feel that love in each piece you bring home 💓⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#briarbaby

node.text:
A bonnet, and so much more. A piece to cherish, to tie lovingly around kissable cheeks as time stands still for a brief, sweet moment; to hold onto with hope and the most tender memories for a future babe. Passing along through siblings and friends and cousins, sharing the same joy and adding new layers of love and nostalgia with each wear, each baby. A tangible piece of a time that goes by too quickly.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Yes, a bonnet; and yet, so much more.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
📸: @the_rasmussens⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#briarbaby
